title: Warlock Master of the Arcane Update 5-RELOADED
description:
Warlock - Master of the Arcane *Update 5* (c) Paradox Interactive
       
            07/2012 :..... RELEASE.DATE .. PROTECTION .......: Steam
                  - :.......... DISC(S) .. GAME.TYPE ........: Strategy
       
      
     
      The latest game in the popular Majesty series, Warlock: Master of the Arcane
      introduces turned-based strategy and global conquest to the fantastic world
      of Ardania. In a time of chaotic upheaval, the player takes the role of a
      great mage, a warlord vying for ultimate power. Your mission is to build an
      empire, expand your borders, research new spells and conquer your enemies.
      Become the ultimate Warlock and rule over all of Ardania!
     
      Read included .txt for a list of what's new.
     

     
     
      1. Unrar into the <install> dir of the game.
      2. Play the game.
      3. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!
